{"tid":944600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲妹直播跳樓自殺…圍觀者歡呼「跳得好！」　警方開始抓人了","createTime":"2018-12-17T09:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T14:21:46.000Z","uid":212399,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"fcef5eed9d1822792f5d094636608322c5c6bb80","tid":944600,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"記者趙蔡州／綜合報導<br />\n中國大陸甘肅省一名19歲李姓女子20日下午時許，爬出當地一間飯店窗外企圖跳樓自殺，結果下方數百名的圍觀民眾竟拍手要她快點跳，李女在僵持4小時後真的跳下喪命，消防員當場發出撕心裂肺的痛哭聲。最後警方決定找出那些鼓吹跳樓的惡劣民眾，目前已經有數人被警方逮捕拘留。<br />\n綜合大陸媒體報導，這位李女2016年9月因為被50歲吳姓老師性侵未遂，校方事後還袒護吳老師不予以處置，某些惡劣同學還在事後嘲笑她，導致她最後罹患上憂鬱症、創傷後壓力症候群等，並且多次企圖自殺未遂，最後得知吳男因罪證不足不起訴，2018年6月20日她才決定跳樓自殺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3371/3371912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3371%2F3371912.jpg&h=74f7493b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3371/3371913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3371%2F3371913.jpg&h=b85d49a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲除了現場圍觀群眾之外，還有許多網友也直播中狠酸。（圖／翻攝微博）<br />\n根據了解，李女爬出飯店8樓窗台外要跳樓時，消防員花了4小時多勸說，試圖讓她放棄跳樓打算，其中一名消防員更試圖上前要把她拉上來，但最後她仍然鬆開了消防員的手，直直從高空掉落重摔在地死亡。李女放手的瞬間也讓消防員當場叫出撕心裂肺的痛哭聲，還用手重擊地板情緒相當懊悔。<br />\n因為當時下方有數百名的圍觀人群，不但沒有幫忙勸說李女回頭，還不停吶喊：「怎麼還不跳」、「把驢都慫栽倒了」、「從一點多跳到六點，還沒跳下來」當李女自殺後還有人說「跳得好！」相當惡劣，消息曝光後也讓許多民眾不滿，警方也決定找出那些惡劣人士，目前已有數人被員警逮捕拘留，警方表示會繼續抓人。<br />\n▼李女放手的瞬間也讓消防員當場叫出撕心裂肺的痛哭聲。（圖／翻攝微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3371/d3371916.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3371%2Fd3371916.jpg&h=6b8bc904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6-Lqj3VK1c4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6-Lqj3VK1c4&d=38KyZA03mmW%2Bd8urcvfUcUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=2b1d16a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6-Lqj3VK1c4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180625/1198979.htm#ixzz5Zvj742cy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180625%2F1198979.htm%23ixzz5Zvj742cy&d=38KyZA03mmW%2Bd8urcvfUcUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b6e6e3c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180625/1198979.htm#ixzz5Zvj742cy</a>"},{"pid":"a8547e066a7ab7adf17f1eabbbea6c0f16ff6f27","tid":944600,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4cf026043878c734a217412f5a45f5b5f420e9","tid":944600,"uid":212399,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:11:50.000Z","msg":"l22歲年輕媽絕望想跳樓　陌生英雄背後摟住她：我們喝杯咖啡！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/casieT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/casieT</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n再一次證明大陸人全部都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f799732a6abce2d44ebe8cb71ba2891a3b35eed","tid":944600,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d102ae5f3ba6adcb8ac0fbc9f87e085b7fa25047","tid":944600,"uid":188264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"唔洗再做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea7b86f9018d0c976164256591ce8028c4a03f5","tid":944600,"uid":4574,"like":17,"dislike":5,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:21:07.000Z","msg":"全世界得支那<br />\n呢個賤種民族睇人仆街"},{"pid":"8bc0769d199b6c2685b9f05bb11906366a8209db","tid":944600,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"跳左未"},{"pid":"deeca64db63d003e6e66a13e39741212f83f4365","tid":944600,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"